- Cash on Hand
- Bank Deposits
- Interest Receivable
- Accounts Receivable
- Inventory

According to the balance sheet:
- Initial value of Total Current Assets: 20000000.00 (as of 2023-12-31)
- End value of Total Current Assets: 21224639.20 (as of 2024-02-05)

These are the assets expected to be realized or consumed within the operating cycle of the business.
